oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Kinsall in Oahu, Hawaii
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Slide film (or reversal film) of Kinsall standing on a dirt road posing for the photograph. There is a military Jeep pulled over on the road. Located in Oahu, Hawaii.
Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall worked as a Command Adjutant while stationed at Hickam Air Force Base in Oahu, Hawaii.
